<h1>Exhibit at TechFair</h1>
<p><strong>MIT TechFair</strong> is a one-day annual technology expo that aims to showcase the world's most innovative tech companies to MIT's best and brightest students. TechFair invites a broad spectrum of companies, from established multinationals to revolutionary new startups, to promote and demonstrate their products to an audience of several thousand MIT students pursuing careers in the industry.</p>
<h2>Tech Talks</h2>
<p>TechFair is proud to announce the addition of <strong>Tech Talks</strong> this year, a series of talks by distinguished speakers from our sponsor companies. Throughout the day, they'll be taking the center stage at TechFair to talk their experiences in the industry, the technology their companies are developing, and - for MIT alumni - their journeys since MIT.</p>
<h2>Sponsorship</h2>
<p>For more information regarding how your company can be a part of TechFair, <a href="/exhibit/packages">read more about sponsorship packages</a>.</p>